however sullivan said he would not venture further on the issue 
until he reviews the recommendations of an advisory committee and 
consults with others about when if ever it might be appropriate to 
use fetal tissue for medical research 
armstrong said he was disappointed in sullivans reply and when 
the time came to vote on sullivans confirmation the senator simply 
voted present 
