international affairs in geneva said the western reaction to irans 
fury over the satanic verses has reinforced khomeinis belief 
that iran is surrounded by a sea of corruption and conspiracies 
it was perfect for him khomeini clearly thinks theres still 
some mileage out of a militant stand against the superpowers 
chubin said in a telephone interview 
the moves by khomeini 88 are a major setback for the 
pragmatists particularly rafsanjani and a boost for hardliners 
who feared rafsanjani was getting too powerful and believed 
