carmela gutierrez she did not give a reason for nazar haros 
resignation and said she didnt know if it had been accepted 
president carlos salinas de gortari appointed nazar haro head of 
mexico citys police intelligence unit shortly after he took office 
in december 
nazar haro 60 spent 20 years with mexicos nowdefunct 
directorate of federal security the equivalent of the fbi he 
resigned on jan 13 1982 when he was indicted in san diego in 
connection with the 84 million international car theft ring 
the ring was smashed in 1981 by the fbi and california police 
fbi agents arrested nazar haro in 1982 after he gave testimomy to 
a federal grand jury investigating the case he was released after 
posting 200000 cash on 1 million bail and he fled to mexico 
in 1983 a us district court judge threw out an 11 million 
libel suit filed by nazar haro against time magazine a story in the 
magazine alleged the us government protected nazar haro from 
prosecution as a car smuggler saying he had been the cias most 
important intelligence source in mexico 
nazar haro has said he cooperated with us officials in criminal 
matters but denied being a paid informant for the cia 
