that since 1981 the number of women appointed to such posts has 
increased 114 percent 
our new study confirms that the message of womens abilities 
and political savvy is being heard by goverors of both parties and 
in all regions of the country said irene natividad head of the 
bipartisan womens political organization 
the survey rated the 50 governors based on the percentage of 
